<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Cody Hatch - Short Posts</title><link href="https://codyhatch.com/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="https://codyhatch.com/feeds/short-posts.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>https://codyhatch.com/</id><updated>2025-02-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><entry><title>Healthcare Spending vs Outcomes</title><link href="https://codyhatch.com/short-posts/healthcare-system-spending-versus-outcomes.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2025-02-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-02-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><author><name>Cody Hatch</name></author><id>tag:codyhatch.com,2025-02-02:/short-posts/healthcare-system-spending-versus-outcomes.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Using data to explore the tradeoffs between healthcare spending, outcomes, and access.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;I was reading in The Economist about &lt;a href="https://www.economist.com/britain/2025/01/30/many-britons-are-waiting-12-hours-at-aande"&gt;wait times for emergency room services in the UK's NHS&lt;/a&gt; and it got me wondering how the NHS compares to several other countries in various healthcare metrics. I decided to compare metrics for the countries listed below, choosing these countries primarily because of the varying ways they implement healthcare, which I'll outline further below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unitied States&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;United Kingdom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Canada&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;France&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Switzerland&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Italy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portugal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I chose to review these countries using primarily three metrics:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average healchare spending per capita (x-axis)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average life expectancy (y-axis)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Median wait time for elective procedures (size of bubble)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is a bubble chart showing the data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;canvas id="myChart"&gt;&lt;/canvas&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
    Chart.register(ChartDataLabels);
    const ctx = document.getElementById('myChart').getContext('2d');
    new Chart(ctx, {
        type: 'bubble',
        data: {
            datasets: [{
                label: 'Healthcare Metrics by Country',
                data: [
                    {x: 12318, y: 76.1, r: 10, country: 'USA'},          // Shorter wait times
                    {x: 5387, y: 80.9, r: 25, country: 'UK'},            // Long wait times
                    {x: 5905, y: 82.3, r: 30, country: 'Canada'},        // Very long wait times
                    {x: 3347, y: 81.1, r: 20, country: 'Portugal'},      // Moderate wait times
                    {x: 3870, y: 82.9, r: 15, country: 'Italy'},         // Moderate-short wait times
                    {x: 5564, y: 82.3, r: 12, country: 'France'},        // Short wait times
                    {x: 9673, y: 83.2, r: 15, country: 'Switzerland'}    // Moderate-short wait times
                ],
                backgroundColor: [
                    'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(153, 102, 255, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(255, 159, 64, 0.5)',
                    'rgba(45, 183, 209, 0.5)'
                ]
            }]
        },
        options: {
            scales: {
                x: {
                    title: {
                        display: true,
                        text: 'Healthcare Spending Per Capita (USD)'
                    }
                },
                y: {
                    title: {
                        display: true,
                        text: 'Life Expectancy (years)'
                    }
                }
            },
            plugins: {
                title: {
                    display: true,
                    text: 'Healthcare Systems: Spending vs Outcomes vs Wait Times',
                    padding: {
                        top: 10,
                        bottom: 5
                    },
                    font: {
                        size: 16,
                        weight: bold
                    }
                },
                subtitle: {
                    display: true,
                    text: 'Bubble size represents median wait times for elective procedures',
                    padding: {
                        top: 5,
                        bottom: 30
                    },
                    font: {
                        size: 12
                    }
                },
                legend: {
                    display: false
                },
                datalabels: {
                    formatter: function(value, context) {
                        return context.dataset.data[context.dataIndex].country;
                    },
                    color: 'black',
                    font: {
                        weight: 'bold'
                    },
                    anchor: 'end',
                    align: 'top',
                    offset: 5
                }
            }
        }
    });
&lt;/script&gt;

